title: SPY'S JEREMY MCGRATH AND JUSTIN BARCIA RIDE HAPPY
description: Happiness knows no boundaries, and neither does Jeremy McGrath or Justin Barcia. Letting loose and tearing apart Cahuilla Creek, MC and Barcia head out for a fun day on the track in the all-new Omen MX with Happy Lens.
